name: Pottery Class
description: Learn how to throw clay in Seattle, WA.

name: Learn to Make Pizza
description: Make pizza by hand in Seattle, WA. Vegan and gluten-free options available.

name: A Twist on Classic Stir Fry
description: Experience asian fusion cuisine in the home of a San Francisco chef.

name: Live Music in Austin, TX
description: Join our afro-funk band as we play in great venues around Austin. Join us for drinks after the performance.

name: Try out the Banjo
description: Get a brief intro to the banjo and tour our tiny home in Austin, TX.

name: Watch a Demo Interpretive Dance
description: Drop in on our dance practice. See professionals work on body movements. Based in NYC.

name: Go Dancing in NYC
description: Go dancing with dancers. We will show you to our favorite clubs in NYC.

name: Youth-Friendly Confidence Course
description: Zip line and team building exercises in the great outdoors of WA state!

name: Indoor Climbing
description: Indoor climbing lesson by experienced climbers in Seattle.

name: 2 Day Climbing Expedition
description: Join us for an extended trip in the Cascades!

name: Tanzania Wildlife Tour
description: Welcome to our home. We maintain an animal shelter outside Dar es Salaam. We will show your our animals and share lunch.

name: Wilderness Course
description: Learn how to start a fire and other key wilderness skills. Based in Portland, OR.

name: Visit an Artist's Studio
description: Visit my studio in Vancouver. I will discuss my process and show you my works in progress at different stages of development.

name: Learn to Paint
description: I will teach you basic color theory and we can discuss abstract composition. But more than anything, this is time to play! Based in Vancouver.

name: Seattle Beer Tour
description: Try out the best craft beer places in Seattle! I am a brewer and will be able to explain the process as we do a series of beer-tastings.

name: Learn to do Henna
description: Do you want to learn henna? I will show you how it is done and you will leave with a beautiful design. Based in Los Angeles.

name: Spring Plants Gardening Lesson
description: Come visit my garden. I am a professional horticulturist and plant enthusiast! I will make you tea and cookies and we can plan your garden design. Based in New Haven, CT.

name: Plant Photography
description: Practice plant photography with me! I am a professional horticulturist and plant enthusiast! I have had my photos featured in Home & Garden. Based in New Haven, CT.

name: Meet my Chameleon
description: Meet Edgar. He is soooo cooooool. Based in Austin, TX.

name: Glitter & Body Paint Party
description: I am a costume artist for the Miami ballet. Meaning I can make you look epic! Mixer at Miami venue to follow (optional).

name: Learn to Make Cake Pops
description: Visit my bakery in Boston, MA. I will show you around, explain how our business operates, and give you lots of taste tests! Finally, we will make cake pops together.

name: Learn to Make Chocolate
description: Visit my bakery in Boston, MA. I will show you around, explain how our business operates, and give you lots of taste tests! Then we'll make some chocolate!

name: Knit with Nancy!
description: Together we will get you started on your own scarf. Wool is local and naturally dyed. Vashon Island, WA.

name: Meet Sheep & Visit Wool Shop
description: We operate a small business out of Vashon, WA where we process wool naturally and use natural dyes. Meet our sheep, they are very friendly!

name: Ride a Horse
description: You're welcome to our ranch for an introduction to equestrian life! Located in Charlottesville, VA

name: Create Bouquets

name: Tour a Florist Shop
description: Learn how I got started as a florist and how we've managed to do what we love!

name: Scuba Dive in Bali
description: Do you love the ocean? We do! Join us for marine adventures in Bali!

name: Snorkel in Bali
description: Do you love the ocean? We do! Join us for marine adventures in Bali!

name: Surf in Bali
description: Do you love the ocean? We do! Join us for marine adventures in Bali!

name: Food Truck Fun!
description: Whether you want to start your own, or just see how we "roll" - come get to know us and have some tasty treats. Based in Portland, OR.

name: Tattoo Artist Studio Tour
description: Come hang out and learn how tattooing is done (well). Cold beer included! Based in Portland, OR.

name: Japanese Garden Design
description: Learn what goes into the design and maintenance of a Japanese garden, with a subject matter expert. Based in Portland, OR.

name: Glass Blowing
description: Visit my Seattle glass-blowing space and watch the process. Get advice on starting the hobby yourself!

name: Craft a Cocktail
description: Learn about mixology! Snacks included.

name: Whole Foods & Wellness Class
description: Join us in our home, as we share how our organic foods business was created and how we live our whole foods lifestyle. Explore our farm and gardens for inspiration, can taste our local wines!

name: Grilling Lesson
description: Become a grilling pro! Experience authentic cuban/creole methods of grilling in New Orleans, LA.
